#. YcLqs
#: 01020300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020300.xhp\n"
"par_id981584288549909\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Properties combine the syntax of procedures and functions. A <literal>Property</literal> usually requires up to one parameter."
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດ (Properties) ເປັນການລວມເອົາໄວຍາກອນຂອງໂປຣຊີເຈີ ແລະ ຟັງຊັນເຂົ້າກັນ. ໂດຍປົກກະຕິ <literal>Property</literal> ຈະຕ້ອງການພາຣາມິເຕີສູງສຸດໜຶ່ງຕົວ."

