#. HrqsB
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Libraries, Modules and Dialogs"
msgstr "ຄັງ (Libraries), ໂໂມດູນ ແລະ ໄດອາລັອກ"

#. vGB4P
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147317\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/01020500.xhp\">Libraries, Modules and Dialogs</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/01020500.xhp\">ຄັງ, ໂໂມດູນ ແລະ ໄດອາລັອກ</link>"

#. 9f6EM
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"par_id3147427\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following describes the basic use of libraries, modules and dialogs in $[officename] Basic."
msgstr "ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແມ່ນການອະທິບາຍກ່ຽວກັບການນຳໃຊ້ ຄັງ, ໂໂມດູນ ແລະ ໄດອາລັອກ ພື້ນຖານໃນ $[officename] Basic."

#. SaxtE
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"par_id3146120\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] Basic provides tools to help you structuring your projects. It supports various \"units\" which enable you to group individual SUBS and FUNCTIONS in a Basic project."
msgstr "$[officename] Basic ມີເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃນການຈັດໂຄງສ້າງໂປຣເຈັກຂອງທ່ານ. ມັນສະໜັບສະໜູນ \"ໜ່ວຍເກັບ\" (units) ຕ່າງໆທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດລວມກຸ່ມ SUBS ແລະ FUNCTIONS ເຂົ້າໃນໂປຣເຈັກ Basic ໄດ້."

#. TZW5m
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148575\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Libraries"
msgstr "ຄັງ (Libraries)"

#. GA9nr
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"par_id3150011\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Libraries serve as a tool for organizing modules, and can either be attached to a document or a template. When the document or a template is saved, all modules contained in the library are automatically saved as well."
msgstr "ຄັງ (Libraries) ເຮັດໜ້າທີ່ເປັນເຄື່ອງມືໃນການຈັດລະບຽບໂມດູນ, ເຊິ່ງສາມາດຕິດໄປກັບເອກະສານ ຫຼື ແມ່ແບບ (template) ໄດ້. ເມື່ອເອກະສານ ຫຼື ແມ່ແບບຖືກບັນທຶກ, ໂມດູນທັງໝົດໃນຄັງກໍຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໄປພ້ອມໆກັນ."

#. iVxPi
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"par_id3151112\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A library can contain up to 16,000 modules."
msgstr "ໜຶ່ງຄັງສາມາດເກັບໂມດູນໄດ້ສູງສຸດ 16,000 ໂມດູນ."

#. GmYip
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149262\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Modules"
msgstr "ໂມດູນ"

#. FFvGa
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"par_id3156441\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A module contains SUBS and FUNCTIONS along with variable declarations. The length of the program that can be saved in a module is limited to 64 kB. If more space is required you can divide a $[officename] Basic project among several modules, and then save them in a single library."
msgstr "ໂມດູນປະກອບດ້ວຍ SUBS ແລະ FUNCTIONS ພ້ອມກັບການປະກາດຕົວແປ. ຄວາມຍາວຂອງໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ບັນທຶກໃນໜຶ່ງໂມດູນແມ່ນຈຳກັດຢູ່ທີ່ 64 kB. ຖ້າຕ້ອງການພື້ນທີ່ຫຼາຍກວ່ານັ້ນ, ທ່ານສາມາດແບ່ງໂປຣເຈັກ $[officename] Basic ອອກເປັນຫຼາຍໆໂມດູນ ແລ້ວບັນທຶກພວກມັນໄວ້ໃນຄັງດຽວກັນ."

#. oo2bB
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152577\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Dialog Modules"
msgstr "ໂມດູນໄດອາລັອກ (Dialog Modules)"

#. GTorM
#: 01020500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020500.xhp\n"
"par_id3149377\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Dialog modules contain dialog definitions, including the dialog box properties, the properties of each dialog element and the events assigned. Since a dialog module can only contain a single dialog, they are often referred to as \"dialogs\"."
msgstr "ໂມດູນໄດອາລັອກປະກອບດ້ວຍການກຳນົດໄດອາລັອກ, ລວມທັງຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງກ່ອງໄດອາລັອກ, ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງແຕ່ລະອົງປະກອບ ແລະ ເຫດການ (events) ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້. ເນື່ອງຈາກໂມດູນໄດອາລັອກສາມາດບັນຈຸໄດ້ພຽງໜຶ່ງໄດອາລັອກເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ພວກມັນຈຶ່ງມັກຖືກເອີ້ນສັ້ນໆວ່າ \"ໄດອາລັອກ\"."

#. konfv
