#. fornx
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3152576\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Tools - Macros - Organize Macros - Basic</emph> and click <emph>Organizer</emph> or click the <emph>Select Module</emph> icon in the Basic IDE to open the <emph>Macro Organizer</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ມາໂຄຣ - ຈັດລະບຽບມາໂຄຣ - Basic</emph> ແລະ ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົວຈັດລະບຽບ</emph> ຫຼື ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ເລືອກໂມດູນ</emph> ໃນ Basic IDE ເພື່ອເປີດໄດອາລັອກ <emph>ຕົວຈັດລະບຽບມາໂຄຣ</emph>."

#. PcnbC
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3153726\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the <emph>Libraries</emph> tab."
msgstr "ຄລິກແຖບ <emph>ໄລບຣາຣີ</emph>."

#. htC8c
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3149664\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select to where you want to attach the library in the <emph>Location</emph> list. If you select Application Macros & Dialogs, the library will belong to the $[officename] application and will be available for all documents. If you select a document the library will be attached to this document and only available from there."
msgstr "ເລືອກບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຄັດຕິດໄລບຣາຣີໃນລາຍການ <emph>ສະຖານທີ່</emph>. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກ ມາໂຄຣ ແລະ ໄດອາລັອກຂອງແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ, ໄລບຣາຣີຈະເປັນຂອງແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ $[officename] ແລະ ຈະນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ກັບທຸກເອກະສານ. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກເອກະສານ ໄລບຣາຣີຈະຖືກຄັດຕິດໃສ່ກັບເອກະສານນັ້ນ ແລະ ນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ຈາກບ່ອນນັ້ນເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. PCjRC
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3153365\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>New</emph> and insert a name to create a new library."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ໃໝ່</emph> ແລະ ໃສ່ຊື່ເພື່ອສ້າງໄລບຣາຣີໃໝ່."

#. 4xPQx
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147394\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Import a Library"
msgstr "ນຳເຂົ້າໄລບຣາຣີ"

#. FfAiG
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3153157\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Tools - Macros - Organize Macros - Basic</emph> and click <emph>Organizer</emph> or click the <emph>Select Module</emph> icon in the Basic IDE to open the <emph>Macro Organizer</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ມາໂຄຣ - ຈັດລະບຽບມາໂຄຣ - Basic</emph> ແລະ ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົວຈັດລະບຽບ</emph> ຫຼື ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ເລືອກໂມດູນ</emph> ໃນ Basic IDE ເພື່ອເປີດໄດອາລັອກ <emph>ຕົວຈັດລະບຽບມາໂຄຣ</emph>."

#. Tkmcd
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3146972\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the <emph>Libraries</emph> tab."
msgstr "ຄລິກແຖບ <emph>ໄລບຣາຣີ</emph>."

#. 7w5hH
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3145640\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select to where you want to import the library in the <emph>Location</emph> list. If you select Application Macros & Dialogs, the library will belong to the $[officename] application and will be available for all documents. If you select a document the library will be imported to this document and only available from there."
msgstr "ເລືອກບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການນຳເຂົ້າໄລບຣາຣີໃນລາຍການ <emph>ສະຖານທີ່</emph>. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກ ມາໂຄຣ ແລະ ໄດອາລັອກຂອງແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ, ໄລບຣາຣີຈະເປັນຂອງແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ $[officename] ແລະ ຈະນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ກັບທຸກເອກະສານ. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກເອກະສານ ໄລບຣາຣີຈະຖືກນຳເຂົ້າໃສ່ເອກະສານນັ້ນ ແລະ ນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ຈາກບ່ອນນັ້ນເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. dUvoX
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3154253\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>Import...</emph> and select an external library to import."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ນຳເຂົ້າ...</emph> ແລະ ເລືອກໄລບຣາຣີພາຍນອກທີ່ຈະນຳເຂົ້າ."

#. 6HMTM
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3154705\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select all libraries to be imported in the <emph>Import Libraries</emph> dialog. The dialog displays all libraries that are contained in the selected file."
msgstr "ເລືອກທຸກໄລບຣາຣີທີ່ຈະນຳເຂົ້າໃນໄດອາລັອກ <emph>ນຳເຂົ້າໄລບຣາຣີ</emph>. ໄດອາລັອກຈະສະແດງທຸກໄລບຣາຣີທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. fahSC
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3163807\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to insert the library as a reference only check the <emph>Insert as reference (read-only)</emph> box. Read-only libraries are fully functional but cannot be modified in the Basic IDE."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກໄລບຣາຣີເປັນການອ້າງອີງເທົ່ານັ້ນ ໃຫ້ໝາຍຕິກໃສ່ຫ້ອງ <emph>ແຊກເປັນການອ້າງອີງ (ອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ)</emph>. ໄລບຣາຣີແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວສາມາດເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ຢ່າງເຕັມທີ່ ແຕ່ບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນ Basic IDE."

#. Rrk55
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3145228\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Check the <emph>Replace existing libraries</emph> box if you want existing libraries of the same name to be overwritten."
msgstr "ໝາຍຕິກໃສ່ຫ້ອງ <emph>ແທນທີ່ໄລບຣາຣີທີ່ມີຢູ່</emph> ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ໄລບຣາຣີທີ່ມີຊື່ຄືກັນຖືກຂຽນທັບ."

#. 8hKDF
#: 01030400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030400.xhp\n"
"par_id3147004\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>OK</emph> to import the library."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph> ເພື່ອນຳເຂົ້າໄລບຣາຣີ."

#. 2AGeq
