#. FQF6P
#: 01050100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01050100.xhp\n"
"par_id3156283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_BASICIDE_WATCHWINDOW_LIST\">Displays the list of watched variables. Click twice with a short pause in between on an entry to edit its value.</ahelp> The new value will be taken as the variable's value for the program."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_BASICIDE_WATCHWINDOW_LIST\">ສະແດງລາຍການຕົວປ່ຽນທີ່ກຳລັງເບິ່ງຄ່າຢູ່. ຄລິກສອງຄັ້ງ (ໂດຍເວັ້ນໄລຍະຫ່າງສັ້ນໆ) ໃສ່ລາຍການເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂຄ່າຂອງມັນ.</ahelp> ຄ່າໃໝ່ນັ້ນຈະຖືກນຳໄປໃຊ້ເປັນຄ່າຂອງຕົວປ່ຽນສຳລັບໂປຣແກຣມ."

