"par_id3153952\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>fileNum</emph>: The data channel number used in the Open statement."
msgstr "<emph>fileNum</emph>: ໝາຍເລກຊ່ອງທາງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນຄຳສັ່ງ Open."

#. FrYvd
#: 03020305.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020305.xhp\n"
"par_id3145366\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>filePos, recordNum</emph>: Position for the next writing or reading. Position can be a number between 1 and 2,147,483,647. According to the file type, the position indicates the number of the record (files in the Random mode) or the byte position (files in the Binary, Output, Append or Input mode). The first byte in a file is position 1, the second byte is position 2, and so on."
msgstr "<emph>filePos, recordNum</emph>: ຕຳແໜ່ງສຳລັບການຂຽນ ຫຼື ການອ່ານຄັ້ງຖັດໄປ. ຕຳແໜ່ງສາມາດເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 1 ຫາ 2,147,483,647. ຕາມປະເພດຂອງໄຟລ໌, ຕຳແໜ່ງຈະບອກໝາຍເລກຂອງລະຄອນ (ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ໃນໂໝດ Random) ຫຼື ຕຳແໜ່ງໄບຕ໌ (ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ໃນໂໝດ Binary, Output, Append ຫຼື Input). ໄບຕ໌ທຳອິດໃນໄຟລ໌ຄືຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ 1, ໄບຕ໌ທີສອງຄືຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ 2, ແລະ ຕໍ່ໆໄປ."

