"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03020401.xhp\">ChDir Statement</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03020401.xhp\">ຄຳສັ່ງ ChDir</link>"

#. yr6FQ
#: 03020401.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020401.xhp\n"
"par_id3153126\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changes the current directory or drive."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ (directory) ຫຼື ໄດຣັຟ (drive) ປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. 9njBT
#: 03020401.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020401.xhp\n"
"par_id461605879610611\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some DOS-specific file and directory functions are no longer provided in %PRODUCTNAME, or their function is only limited. For example, support for the <literal>ChDir</literal>, <literal>ChDrive</literal> and <literal>CurDir</literal> functions is not provided. Some DOS-specific properties are no longer used in functions that expect file properties as parameters (for example, to differentiate from concealed files and system files). This ensures the greatest possible level of platform independence for %PRODUCTNAME. Therefore this feature is subject to removal in a future release."
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີບາງຢ່າງທີ່ສະເພາະກັບ DOS ຈະບໍ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ອີກຕໍ່ໄປ, ຫຼື ການເຮັດວຽກຂອງພວກມັນຈະຖືກຈຳກັດ. ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ, ຈະບໍ່ຮອງຮັບຟັງຊັນ <literal>ChDir</literal>, <literal>ChDrive</literal> ແລະ <literal>CurDir</literal>. ຄຸນສົມບັດສະເພາະ DOS ບາງຢ່າງຈະບໍ່ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນຟັງຊັນທີ່ຕ້ອງການຄຸນສົມບັດໄຟລ໌ເປັນພາຣາມິເຕີ (ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ, ເພື່ອແຍກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຖືກເຊື່ອງ ແລະ ໄຟລ໌ລະບົບ). ນີ້ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນໃຫ້ %PRODUCTNAME ສາມາດເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ໃນທຸກແພລັດຟອມຢ່າງເປັນອິດສະຫຼະທີ່ສຸດ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ຄຸນສົມບັດນີ້ອາດຈະຖືກຕັດອອກໃນລຸ້ນຕໍ່ໆໄປ."

#. e4feF
#: 03020401.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020401.xhp\n"
"par_id321620859565917\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/lib_ScriptForge.xhp\">ScriptForge</link> library in %PRODUCTNAME 7.1 introduces the <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_filesystem.xhp\">FileSystem</link> service with methods to handle files and folders in user scripts."
msgstr "ໄລບຣາຣີ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/lib_ScriptForge.xhp\">ScriptForge</link> ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME 7.1 ໄດ້ແນະນຳບໍລິການ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_filesystem.xhp\">FileSystem</link> ພ້ອມກັບວິທີການຕ່າງໆໃນການຈັດການໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີໃນສະຄຣິບຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#. WXPPp
#: 03020401.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020401.xhp\n"
"par_id3153897\n"
"help.text"
msgid "ChDir Text As String"
msgstr "ChDir Text As String"

#. QhhVQ
#: 03020401.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020401.xhp\n"
"par_id3150543\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Text:</emph> Any string expression that specifies the directory path or drive."
msgstr "<emph>Text:</emph> ນິພົດສະຕຣິງໃດໜຶ່ງທີ່ກຳນົດເສັ້ນທາງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ ຫຼື ໄດຣັຟ."

#. 8bbhs
#: 03020401.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020401.xhp\n"
"par_id3152598\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you only want to change the current drive, enter the drive letter followed by a colon."
msgstr "ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນພຽງແຕ່ໄດຣັຟປັດຈຸບັນ, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຕົວອັກສອນໄດຣັຟແລ້ວຕາມດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຈ້ຳສອງ ( : )."

#. vRQAc
