"03020406.xhp\n"
"par_id3146957\n"
"help.text"
msgid "FileCopy Source As String, Destination As String"
msgstr "FileCopy Source As String, Destination As String"

#. CjRbT
#: 03020406.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020406.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153825\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Parameters:"
msgstr "ພາຣາມິເຕີ:"

#. D3o4o
#: 03020406.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020406.xhp\n"
"par_id3155390\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Source</emph>: Any string expression that specifies the name of the file that you want to copy. The expression can contain optional path and drive information. If you want, you can enter a path in <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/00000002.xhp\">URL notation</link>."
msgstr "<emph>Source</emph>: ນິພົດສະຕຣິງໃດໜຶ່ງທີ່ກຳນົດຊື່ຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສຳເນົາ. ນິພົດສາມາດມີຂໍ້ມູນເສັ້ນທາງ ແລະ ໄດຣັຟໄດ້. ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການ, ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນເສັ້ນທາງໃນ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/00000002.xhp\">ຮູບແບບ URL</link> ໄດ້."

#. b2bKE
#: 03020406.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020406.xhp\n"
"par_id3150669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Destination</emph>: Any string expression that specifies where you want to copy the source file to. The expression can contain the destination drive, the path, and file name, or the path in URL notation."
msgstr "<emph>Destination</emph>: ນິພົດສະຕຣິງໃດໜຶ່ງທີ່ກຳນົດບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສຳເນົາໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນທາງໄປຫາ. ນິພົດສາມາດປະກອບມີໄດຣັຟປາຍທາງ, ເສັ້ນທາງ, ແລະ ຊື່ໄຟລ໌, ຫຼື ເສັ້ນທາງໃນຮູບແບບ URL."

#. WgMEt
#: 03020406.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020406.xhp\n"
"par_id3150791\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can only use the FileCopy statement to copy files that are not opened."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ FileCopy ເພື່ອສຳເນົາໄຟລ໌ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ເປີດຢູ່ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. kPKuG
