#. kC2pZ
#: 03020407.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020407.xhp\n"
"par_id3159153\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Text:</emph> Any string expression that contains an unambiguous (no wildcards) file specification. You can also use <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/00000002.xhp\">URL notation</link>."
msgstr "<emph>Text:</emph> ນິພົດສະຕຣິງໃດໜຶ່ງທີ່ກຳນົດໄຟລ໌ຢ່າງຊັດເຈນ (ບໍ່ໃຊ້ wildcards). ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/00000002.xhp\">ຮູບແບບ URL</link> ໄດ້."

#. qqouA
#: 03020407.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03020407.xhp\n"
"par_id3155306\n"
