msgctxt ""
"03080103.xhp\n"
"par_id3145786\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Number:</emph> Numeric expression that defines the angle in radians that you want to calculate the sine for."
msgstr "<emph>ຕົວເລກ:</emph> ສຳນວນຕົວເລກທີ່ກຳນົດຄ່າມຸມເປັນເຣດຽນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຄຳນວນຫາຄ່າຊາຍ."

