"par_id3155413\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To convert degrees to radians, multiply degrees by <literal>Pi</literal>/180, and to convert radians to degrees, multiply radians by 180/<literal>Pi</literal>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອແປງອົງສາເປັນເຣດຽນ, ໃຫ້ຄູນອົງສາດ້ວຍ <literal>Pi</literal>/180, ແລະ ເພື່ອແປງເຣດຽນເປັນອົງສາ, ໃຫ້ຄູນເຣດຽນດ້ວຍ 180/<literal>Pi</literal>."

