"03080202.xhp\n"
"par_id3153968\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can calculate logarithms to any base (n) for any number (x) by dividing the natural logarithm of x by the natural logarithm of n, as follows:"
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຄຳນວນຫາລໍກາຣິດຖານໃດກໍໄດ້ (n) ສຳລັບຕົວເລກໃດໜຶ່ງ (x) ໂດຍການຫານລໍກາຣິດທຳມະຊາດຂອງ x ດ້ວຍລໍກາຣິດທຳມະຊາດຂອງ n ດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. 43ZUC
#: 03080202.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03080202.xhp\n"
"par_id3145420\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Log<sub>n</sub>(x) = Log(x) / Log(n)"
msgstr "Log<sub>n</sub>(x) = Log(x) / Log(n)"

