"par_id3147226\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following statements execute loops."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃຊ້ສຳລັບປະມວນຜົນວົງຈອນ."

#. UAuBq
