#. C2e3R
#: 03090202.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03090202.xhp\n"
"par_id3156286\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In nested <emph>For...Next</emph> loops, if you exit a loop unconditionally with <emph>Exit For</emph>, only one loop is exited."
msgstr "ໃນວົງຈອນ <emph>For...Next</emph> ທີ່ຊ້ອນກັນ, ຖ້າທ່ານອອກຈາກວົງຈອນແບບບໍ່ມີເງື່ອນໄຂດ້ວຍ <emph>Exit For</emph>, ມັນຈະອອກຈາກວົງຈອນພຽງຊັ້ນດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

