#. X2mAh
#: 03090301.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03090301.xhp\n"
"par_id3153190\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the program encounters a Return statement not preceded by <emph>GoSub</emph>, $[officename] Basic returns an error message. Use <emph>Exit Sub</emph> or <emph>Exit Function</emph> to ensure that the program leaves a Sub or Function before reaching the next Return statement."
msgstr "ຖ້າໂປຣແກຣມພົບຄຳສັ່ງ Return ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຕາມຫຼັງ <emph>GoSub</emph>, $[officename] Basic ຈະສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມຜິດພາດ. ໃຊ້ <emph>Exit Sub</emph> ຫຼື <emph>Exit Function</emph> ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າໂປຣແກຣມຈະອອກຈາກ Sub ຫຼື Function ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະໄປຮອດຄຳສັ່ງ Return ຖັດໄປ."

#. HZDqC
#: 03090301.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03090301.xhp\n"
"par_id3145799\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following example demonstrates the use of <emph>GoSub</emph> and <emph>Return</emph>. By executing a program section twice, the program calculates the square root of two numbers that are entered by the user."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນການໃຊ້ <emph>GoSub</emph> ແລະ <emph>Return</emph>. ໂດຍການປະມວນຜົນສ່ວນຂອງໂປຣແກຣມສອງຄັ້ງ, ໂປຣແກຣມຈະຄິດໄລ່ຮາກຂັ້ນສອງຂອງສອງຕົວເລກທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ປ້ອນເຂົ້າ."

