msgctxt ""
"03120411.xhp\n"
"par_id3153990\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns the position of a string within another string, starting from the right side of the string."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມພາຍໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມອື່ນ, ໂດຍເລີ່ມຈາກເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. vY8DG
#: 03120411.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03120411.xhp\n"
"par_id3147303\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The InStrRev function returns the position at which the match was found, from the right. If the string was not found, the function returns 0."
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນ InStrRev ສົ່ງຄືນຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ພົບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ກົງກັນ ໂດຍນັບຈາກເບື້ອງຂວາ. ຖ້າບໍ່ພົບຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ຟັງຊັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນ 0."

