"par_id31541255547\n"
"help.text"
msgid "iPos = InStrRev(sInput,\"the\",10,1) ' Returns 1, search is case-insensitive"
msgstr "iPos = InStrRev(sInput,\"the\",10,1) ' ສົ່ງຄືນ 1, ການຄົ້ນຫາແບບບໍ່ຈຳແນກຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍ"

#. Yxhru
