msgctxt ""
"03140012.xhp\n"
"par_id240720170144225698\n"
"help.text"
msgid "REM Calculate the yearly depreciation of an asset that cost $10,000 at"
msgstr "REM ຄິດໄລ່ຄ່າຫຼຸ້ຍຫ້ຽນລາຍປີຂອງສິນຊັບທີ່ມີຕົ້ນທຶນ $10,000 ໃນ"

#. u9ABj
#: 03140012.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03140012.xhp\n"
"par_id240720170144223210\n"
"help.text"
msgid "REM the start of year 1, and has a salvage value of $1,000 after 5 years."
msgstr "REM ຕອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງປີທີ 1, ແລະ ມີມູນຄ່າຊາກ $1,000 ຫຼັງຈາກ 5 ປີ."

#. 898Jk
#: 03140012.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03140012.xhp\n"
"par_id240720170144223139\n"
"help.text"
msgid "REM Calculate the depreciation during year 1."
msgstr "REM ຄິດໄລ່ຄ່າຫຼຸ້ຍຫ້ຽນໃນລະຫວ່າງປີທີ 1."

