#. AVhyb
#: Resume.xhp
msgctxt ""
"Resume.xhp\n"
"N0003\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Resets error information and indicates what to execute next."
msgstr "ລ້າງຂໍ້ມູນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ ແລະ ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ເຮັດຫຍັງຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. FhZm3
