"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0083\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"classmodulestatement\"><link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/classmodule.xhp\">Option ClassModule Statement</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"classmodulestatement\"><link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/classmodule.xhp\">ຄຳສັ່ງ Option ClassModule</link></variable>"

#. 4MQj9
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0084\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies that the module is a class module that contains members, properties, procedures and functions."
msgstr "ລະບຸວ່າໂມດູນນີ້ແມ່ນຄລາສໂມດູນ (class module) ທີ່ປະກອບດ້ວຍສະມາຊິກ, ຄຸນສົມບັດ, ຂັ້ນຕອນ ແລະ ຟັງຊັນ."

#. vqr43
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0089\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This statement must be used jointly with <literal>Option Compatible</literal> statement or <literal>Option VBASupport 1</literal>, the former is enabling VBA compatibility mode, while the latter is enforcing VBA support on top of compatibility."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັບຄຳສັ່ງ <literal>Option Compatible</literal> ຫຼື <literal>Option VBASupport 1</literal>, ໂດຍແບບທຳອິດຈະເປີດນຳໃຊ້ໂໝດເຂົ້າກັນໄດ້ກັບ VBA, ໃນຂະນະທີ່ແບບຫຼັງຈະບັງຄັບການຮອງຮັບ VBA ເພີ່ມເຕີມຈາກຄວາມເຂົ້າກັນໄດ້."

#. UoERn
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0095\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' Optional members go here"
msgstr "' ໃສ່ສະມາຊິກທາງເລືອກຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້"

#. 4Ffze
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0098\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' Optional construction code goes here"
msgstr "' ໃສ່ລະຫັດການສ້າງ (construction code) ທາງເລືອກຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້"

#. K5DSq
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0099\n"
"help.text"
msgid "End Sub ' Constructor"
msgstr "End Sub ' ຕົວສ້າງ (Constructor)"

#. PwJxP
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0101\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' Optional destruction code goes here"
msgstr "' ໃສ່ລະຫັດການທຳລາຍ (destruction code) ທາງເລືອກຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້"

#. AmeAe
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0102\n"
"help.text"
msgid "End Sub ' Destructor"
msgstr "End Sub ' ຕົວທຳລາຍ (Destructor)"

#. Lsaqg
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0104\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' Properties go here."
msgstr "' ໃສ່ຄຸນສົມບັດຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້."

#. RFy5k
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0106\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' Procedures & functions go here."
msgstr "' ໃສ່ຂັ້ນຕອນ ແລະ ຟັງຊັນຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້."

#. Funka
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0108\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Refer to <link href=\"text/sbasic/python/python_platform.xhp\">Identifying the Operating System</link> and <link href=\"text/sbasic/python/python_session.xhp\">Getting Session Information</link> for class module simple examples."
msgstr "ເບິ່ງທີ່ <link href=\"text/sbasic/python/python_platform.xhp\">ການລະບຸລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ</link> ແລະ <link href=\"text/sbasic/python/python_session.xhp\">ການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນເຊດຊັນ</link> ສຳລັບຕົວຢ່າງງ່າຍໆຂອງຄລາສໂມດູນ."

#. JQJqh
#: classmodule.xhp
msgctxt ""
"classmodule.xhp\n"
"N0109\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Multiple thorough class examples are available from <link href=\"text/sbasic/guide/access2base.xhp\">Access2Base shared Basic library</link>."
msgstr "ມີຕົວຢ່າງຄລາສທີ່ລະອຽດຫຼາຍຕົວຢ່າງໃນ <link href=\"text/sbasic/guide/access2base.xhp\">ໄລບຣາຣີ Basic ທີ່ໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັນຂອງ Access2Base</link>."

#. vSapF
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Collection Object"
msgstr "ອັອບເຈັກຄໍເລັກຊັນ (Collection Object)"

#. TdXDY
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"bm_id3149205\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>Collection Object</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ອັອບເຈັກຄໍເລັກຊັນ (Collection Object)</bookmark_value>"

#. zhFUm
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"hd_id791633472607429\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"Collection_h1\"><link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/collection.xhp\">Collection Object</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"Collection_h1\"><link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/collection.xhp\">ອັອບເຈັກຄໍເລັກຊັນ</link></variable>"

#. 7xSei
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id581633961735332\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Collections can be used to store items of different types. Each item can be accessed by its index or by an optional key associated with it."
msgstr "ຄໍເລັກຊັນສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອຈັດເກັບລາຍການປະເພດຕ່າງໆ. ແຕ່ລະລາຍການສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ໂດຍຜ່ານດັດຊະນີ ຫຼື ໂດຍຄີ (key) ທາງເລືອກທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບມັນ."

#. 9b4kg
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id131633961959816\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A <literal>Collection</literal> object has the following methods:"
msgstr "ອັອບເຈັກ <literal>Collection</literal> ມີເມທອດ (methods) ດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. XoLQr
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id331633962000259\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Add:</emph> inserts a new item into the collection. Optionally a string value can be defined as the key to the item."
msgstr "<emph>Add:</emph> ແຊກລາຍການໃໝ່ເຂົ້າໃນຄໍເລັກຊັນ. ສາມາດກຳນົດຄ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມເປັນຄີ (key) ໃຫ້ກັບລາຍການໄດ້."

#. ddAGy
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id181633962000767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Count:</emph> returns the number of items in the collection."
msgstr "<emph>Count:</emph> ສົ່ງຄືນຈຳນວນລາຍການທັງໝົດໃນຄໍເລັກຊັນ."

#. ad7qY
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id521633962001072\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Item:</emph> returns the item in the collection by passing its index or key."
msgstr "<emph>Item:</emph> ສົ່ງຄືນລາຍການໃນຄໍເລັກຊັນໂດຍການລະບຸດັດຊະນີ ຫຼື ຄີ."

#. GX6nx
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id981633962001272\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Remove:</emph> removes the specified item from the collection by its index or key."
msgstr "<emph>Remove:</emph> ລຶບລາຍການທີ່ລະບຸອອກຈາກຄໍເລັກຊັນໂດຍໃຊ້ດັດຊະນີ ຫຼື ຄີ."

#. yyWx7
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id221633976539661\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Items in a Collection can be accessed either by their indices (as in a 1-based single-dimensional Array) or by their associated keys."
msgstr "ລາຍການໃນຄໍເລັກຊັນສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ທັງຜ່ານດັດຊະນີ (ຄືກັນກັບອາເຣມິຕິດຽວທີ່ເລີ່ມຈາກ 1) ຫຼື ຜ່ານຄີທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. FyEKE
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id811634214809970\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_dictionary.xhp\"><literal>ScriptForge Dictionary</literal></link> service extends the <literal>Collection</literal> object by providing supplemental features as key retrieval and replacement, as well as import/export to Array objects and JSON strings."
msgstr "ບໍລິການ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_dictionary.xhp\"><literal>ScriptForge Dictionary</literal></link> ໄດ້ຂະຫຍາຍຄວາມສາມາດຂອງອັອບເຈັກ <literal>Collection</literal> ໂດຍການເພີ່ມຄຸນສົມບັດຕ່າງໆ ເຊັ່ນ ການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ການປ່ຽນແທນຄີ, ລວມທັງການນຳເຂົ້າ/ສົ່ງອອກເປັນອັອບເຈັກອາເຣ (Array) ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມ JSON."

#. pJAht
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"hd_id51633962353863\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating a Collection"
msgstr "ການສ້າງຄໍເລັກຊັນ"

#. 28i8B
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id491633962366024\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To create a <literal>Collection</literal> use the <literal>New</literal> keyword. The following example creates a <literal>Collection</literal> object and populates it with three items:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອສ້າງ <literal>Collection</literal> ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຄຳຫຼັກ <literal>New</literal>. ຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ຈະສ້າງອັອບເຈັກ <literal>Collection</literal> ແລະ ເພີ່ມລາຍການເຂົ້າໄປ 3 ລາຍການ:"

#. 8hHmz
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"hd_id421633962742512\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adding Items"
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມລາຍການ"

#. 3qnWY
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id261633962766238\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <literal>Add</literal> method can be used to add new items into the <literal>Collection</literal> object."
msgstr "ເມທອດ <literal>Add</literal> ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອເພີ່ມລາຍການໃໝ່ເຂົ້າໃນອັອບເຈັກ <literal>Collection</literal>."

#. htAaY
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id501633974650241\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>item:</emph> the item to be added to the <literal>Collection</literal>. May be of any type."
msgstr "<emph>item:</emph> ລາຍການທີ່ຈະເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ <literal>Collection</literal>. ສາມາດເປັນປະເພດໃດກໍໄດ້."

#. DUGrx
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id181633974650705\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>key:</emph> string value used as the unique key used to identify this value."
msgstr "<emph>key:</emph> ຄ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ໃຊ້ເປັນຄີທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນເພື່ອລະບຸຄ່ານີ້."

#. yoEzK
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id391633974651050\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>before, after:</emph> optional keyword argument that indicates where the new item will be placed in the <literal>Collection</literal>. Only one of the arguments <literal>before</literal> or <literal>after</literal> can be specified to determine the index or key before which (or after which) the new item is to be placed."
msgstr "<emph>before, after:</emph> ອາກິວເມັນທາງເລືອກທີ່ລະບຸວ່າລາຍການໃໝ່ຈະຖືກວາງໄວ້ບ່ອນໃດໃນ <literal>Collection</literal>. ສາມາດລະບຸໄດ້ພຽງແຕ່ <literal>before</literal> ຫຼື <literal>after</literal> ຢ່າງໃດຢ່າງໜຶ່ງ ເພື່ອກຳນົດດັດຊະນີ ຫຼື ຄີ ທີ່ລາຍການໃໝ່ຈະຖືກວາງໄວ້ກ່ອນໜ້າ ຫຼື ຖັດຈາກນັ້ນ."

#. xcdEF
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id211633962988398\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The example below adds two elements into a <literal>Collection</literal>. The first has a key associated with it, whereas the second does not."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ຈະເພີ່ມ 2 ອົງປະກອບເຂົ້າໃນ <literal>Collection</literal>. ອັນທຳອິດມີຄີກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ, ສ່ວນອັນທີສອງແມ່ນບໍ່ມີ."

#. ZKBEQ
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id71633963110632\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <literal>Add</literal> method also supports keyword arguments:"
msgstr "ເມທອດ <literal>Add</literal> ຍັງຮອງຮັບອາກິວເມັນແບບຄຳຫຼັກ (keyword arguments):"

#. ZhTZb
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id941633963225913\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keys must be unique in a <literal>Collection</literal> object. Comparison between keys is <emph>case-insensitive</emph>. Adding duplicated keys will result in a runtime error."
msgstr "ຄີ (Keys) ຕ້ອງບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນໃນອັອບເຈັກ <literal>Collection</literal>. ການປຽບທຽບຄີແມ່ນ <emph>ບໍ່ສົນໃຈຕົວອັກສອນໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍ</emph>. ການເພີ່ມຄີທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນເວລາເຮັດວຽກ (runtime error)."

#. NVgmj
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id891633975568372\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The example below illustrates how to use the <literal>Before</literal> and <literal>After</literal> keyword arguments to determine the position of the item that is being added."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ສະແດງວິທີໃຊ້ <literal>Before</literal> ແລະ <literal>After</literal> ເພື່ອກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງລາຍການທີ່ກຳລັງເພີ່ມ."

#. WxjE9
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id121633976325472\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Items in a <literal>Collection</literal> object are assigned an integer index value that starts at 1 and corresponds to the order in which they were added."
msgstr "ລາຍການໃນອັອບເຈັກ <literal>Collection</literal> ຈະຖືກກຳນົດຄ່າດັດຊະນີເປັນໂຕເລກຈຳນວນຖ້ວນ ເລີ່ມຈາກ 1 ຕາມລຳດັບການເພີ່ມ."

#. 2Lrc6
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"hd_id141633977141797\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Accessing Items"
msgstr "ການເຂົ້າເຖິງລາຍການ"

#. MquEn
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id431633977156315\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the <literal>Item</literal> method to access a given item by its index or key."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ເມທອດ <literal>Item</literal> ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງລາຍການທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍດັດຊະນີ ຫຼື ຄີ."

#. DCFTg
#: collection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collection.xhp\n"
"par_id261633976447187\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>index:</emph> an integer value specifying the index of the item to be returned."
msgstr "<emph>index:</emph> ຄ່າໂຕເລກຈຳນວນຖ້ວນທີ່ລະບຸດັດຊະນີຂອງລາຍການທີ່ຈະສົ່ງຄືນ."

