#. wJZW9
#: enum.xhp
msgctxt ""
"enum.xhp\n"
"par_id731573636687662\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enumerations can be extended to other data types using <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03090413.xhp\">Type statement</link> definitions. <link href=\"text/sbasic/guide/basic_2_python.xhp\">Calling Python Scripts from Basic</link> illustrates that mechanism."
msgstr "Enum ສາມາດຂະຫຍາຍໄປສູ່ປະເພດຂໍ້ມູນອື່ນໆໄດ້ໂດຍການໃຊ້ການກຳນົດ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03090413.xhp\">ຄຳສັ່ງ Type</link>. <link href=\"text/sbasic/guide/basic_2_python.xhp\">ການຮຽກໃຊ້ Python Scripts ຈາກ Basic</link> ຈະສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເຖິງກົນໄກນັ້ນ."

