#. mwGMA
#: is_keyword.xhp
msgctxt ""
"is_keyword.xhp\n"
"par_id3145090\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Tests if two Basic variables refer to the same object instance."
msgstr "ທົດສອບວ່າຕົວປ່ຽນ Basic ສອງຕົວອ້າງອີງເຖິງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ (instance) ຂອງອັອບເຈັກດຽວກັນຫຼືບໍ່."

#. HTVQA
#: is_keyword.xhp
msgctxt ""
"is_keyword.xhp\n"
"par_id441633531311929\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <literal>oObj1</literal> and <literal>oObj2</literal> are references to the same object instance, the result will be <emph>True</emph>."
msgstr "ຖ້າ <literal>oObj1</literal> ແລະ <literal>oObj2</literal> ແມ່ນການອ້າງອີງເຖິງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງອັອບເຈັກດຽວກັນ, ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຈະເປັນ <emph>True</emph>."

#. akugg
#: is_keyword.xhp
msgctxt ""
"is_keyword.xhp\n"
"par_id771633473462939\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The example below first defines a new type <literal>Student</literal>. Calling <literal>TestObjects</literal> creates the object <literal>oStudent1</literal> as a new object of this type."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ທຳອິດຈະກຳນົດປະເພດໃໝ່ <literal>Student</literal>. ເມື່ອຮຽກໃຊ້ <literal>TestObjects</literal> ຈະສ້າງອັອບເຈັກ <literal>oStudent1</literal> ເປັນອັອບເຈັກໃໝ່ຂອງປະເພດນີ້."

#. mAAho
#: is_keyword.xhp
msgctxt ""
"is_keyword.xhp\n"
"par_id841633532400710\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The assignment <literal>oStudent2 = oStudent1</literal> actually copies the reference to the same object. Hence the result of applying the <literal>Is</literal> operator is <emph>True</emph>."
msgstr "ການກຳນົດຄ່າ <literal>oStudent2 = oStudent1</literal> ແມ່ນການສຳເນົາການອ້າງອີງໄປຍັງອັອບເຈັກດຽວກັນ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ຜົນຂອງການໃຊ້ຕົວດຳເນີນການ <literal>Is</literal> ຈຶ່ງເປັນ <emph>True</emph>."

#. mvVuR
#: is_keyword.xhp
msgctxt ""
"is_keyword.xhp\n"
"par_id181633473874216\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The example below returns <emph>False</emph> because <literal>oStudent1</literal> and <literal>oStudent2</literal> are references to two different object instances, each created with the <literal>New</literal> operator."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ຈະສົ່ງຄືນ <emph>False</emph> ເພາະວ່າ <literal>oStudent1</literal> ແລະ <literal>oStudent2</literal> ແມ່ນການອ້າງອີງເຖິງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງອັອບເຈັກທີ່ຕ່າງກັນ, ເຊິ່ງແຕ່ລະຕົວຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວດຳເນີນການ <literal>New</literal>."

